The paper deals with program analysis and static analysis of heap data, which are topics that fall under the programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories. The paper also proposes new analyses for heap data, which could fall under the logic in computer science (cs.LO) sub-category. The use of access graphs and data flow analysis could also fall under the data structures (cs.DS) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions an application for garbage collection, which could fall under the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
